'From Cuis 3.2 of 12 April 2011 [latest update: #914] on 19 May 2011 at 11:23:15 am'!!ContentPack methodsFor: 'converting' stamp: 'cbr 5/19/2011 10:45'!asContentPack: aDictionary	"Recursively make ContentPacks of all objects which include behavior from Dictionary."	| associations |	associations _ aDictionary keys collect: [ :key | 		((aDictionary at: key) class includesBehavior: Dictionary)			ifTrue: [ key -> (self asContentPack: (aDictionary at: key)) ]			ifFalse: [ key -> (aDictionary at: key) ]		].	^ associations as: ContentPack! !